            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Dilectissimo et valde <supplied reason="lost">desiderabili domino fratri <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied><lb break="no" n="2"/>lerio Marcellinus peccator <supplied reason="lost">in <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>o</ex><abbr>m</abbr><ex>in</ex>o</expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>alutem</ex></expan> cogor fraternita</supplied><lb break="no" n="3"/>tem tuam monere qua expos<supplied reason="lost">tulo</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="4"/>promisisti mihi dare de re<supplied reason="lost">ditibus <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> dic</supplied><lb break="no" n="5"/>es quare numquid aliqui<supplied reason="lost">d defuit vobis an nescis quod di</supplied><lb break="no" n="6"/>cit scribtura <note>sic</note> os qui <note>sic</note> men<supplied reason="lost">titur occidit animam et iterum</supplied> <lb n="7"/>perdes eos qui locuntur m<supplied reason="lost">endacium <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> si</supplied><lb break="no" n="8"/>cut s<expan><ex>an</ex><abbr>c</abbr><ex>tu</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> euangilius <note>sic</note> dicit sermo <supplied reason="lost">vester sit est est non non</supplied> <lb n="9"/>quod autem abundantius es<supplied reason="lost">t a malo est verumtamen ego in</supplied> <lb n="10"/>hominem non spero sed mag<supplied reason="lost">is in <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>o</ex><abbr>m</abbr><ex>in</ex>o</expan> confisus sum sicut di</supplied><lb break="no" n="11"/>cit profeta <note>sic</note> nolite confidere <supplied reason="lost">in principibus in filiis</supplied> <lb n="12"/>hominum in quibus non est sa<supplied reason="lost">lus et iterum dicit bonum est</supplied> <lb n="13"/>confidere in D<expan><ex>o</ex><abbr>m</abbr><ex>in</ex><abbr>o</abbr></expan> quam confid<supplied reason="lost">ere in homine bonum est spe</supplied><lb break="no" n="14"/>rare in D<expan><ex>o</ex><abbr>mi</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>o</abbr></expan> quam sperare in pri<supplied reason="lost">ncipibus veniam et salu</supplied><lb break="no" n="15"/>tem m<supplied reason="lost">ic</supplied>hi <note>sic</note> D<expan><ex>o</ex><abbr>m</abbr><ex>inu</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> tuis precibus mi<supplied reason="lost">tigatus donare dignetur</supplied>
            </ab></div>
